# GODM - Render Environment Variables Template
#
# IMPORTANT: DO NOT commit actual values to Git!
#
# HOW TO USE:
# 1. Go to Render Dashboard → Your Service → Environment tab
# 2. Click "Add Environment Variable" for each variable below
# 3. Copy the KEY name and enter your actual VALUE
# 4. Never commit the actual values to your repository
#
# SYSTEM CONFIGURATION (Auto-set by render.yaml)
# These are automatically configured - don't set manually:
# NODE_ENV=production (set in render.yaml)
# AUTO_MIGRATE=true (set in render.yaml)
# PORT=auto-assigned by Render
# REDIS_URL=auto-connected from Redis service

#
# VARIABLES TO SET MANUALLY IN RENDER DASHBOARD:
# ===============================================

# Instagram/Facebook API Configuration
# Get these from Facebook Developers Console (https://developers.facebook.com)
INSTAGRAM_CLIENT_ID=your_facebook_app_id_here
INSTAGRAM_CLIENT_SECRET=your_facebook_app_secret_here
FACEBOOK_APP_ID=your_facebook_app_id_here
FACEBOOK_APP_SECRET=your_facebook_app_secret_here

# Instagram Business Account Configuration
INSTAGRAM_BUSINESS_ACCOUNT_ID=your_instagram_business_account_id
INSTAGRAM_BOT_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_long_lived_page_access_token

# OAuth Redirect URI (update with your actual Render frontend URL)
INSTAGRAM_REDIRECT_URI=https://your-frontend-url.onrender.com/auth/callback

# Webhook Configuration
# Create a secure random string for webhook verification
WEBHOOK_VERIFY_TOKEN=your_secure_webhook_verify_token_here

# ===============================================
# STEP-BY-STEP SETUP:
# ===============================================
# 1. Go to https://dashboard.render.com
# 2. Select your 'godm-backend' service
# 3. Click 'Environment' tab
# 4. Click 'Add Environment Variable'
# 5. For each variable above:
#    - Key: Copy the name (e.g., INSTAGRAM_CLIENT_ID)
#    - Value: Enter your actual value (not the placeholder)
# 6. Save each variable
# 7. Redeploy your service

# ===============================================
# SECURITY REMINDERS:
# ===============================================
# ✅ Set variables in Render Dashboard only
# ✅ Never commit actual values to Git
# ✅ Use strong, unique tokens
# ✅ Enable 2FA on Facebook Developer account
# ✅ Rotate tokens regularly